            <div class="p-3 bg-violet-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-violet-800 dark:text-violet-300 rounded-lg text-center border border-violet-100 dark:border-violet-800 hover:bg-violet-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition">Python (Django)</div>
            <div class="p-3 bg-violet-50 dark:bg-gray-700 text-violet-800 dark:text-violet-300 rounded-lg text-center border border-violet-100 dark:border-violet-800 hover:bg-violet-100 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition">React JS</div>
